{"tid":2131902,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【內循環】華為次季手機出貨首度超越三星 , 7成買家在中國","createTime":"2020-07-30T06:36:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T04:58:25.000Z","uid":25468,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"97cfac8777cffa5ead286a28942fb1ab65d340e1","tid":2131902,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:36:33.000Z","msg":"研究公司Canalys報告，華為今年第二季在全球市場的智能手機出貨量首度超越三星，成為全球出貨量冠軍。主要受惠中國地區的銷售，其國際業務則受到美國制裁的影響。<br />\n<br />\n報告指，華為第二季的智能手機出貨量為5,580萬部，較去年同期下滑5%；三星第二季智能手機出貨量為5,370萬部，較去年同期大減30%。當中，華為第二季在中國銷售超過70%的智能手機，反觀其他國際市場的手機出貨量較去年同期下降27%。<br />\n<br />\nCanalys分析師Mo Jia指出，歐洲等各地的關鍵渠道夥伴對華為設備的疑慮增加，或將採用其他品牌降低風險，長期來看，華為難保此一領先地位，且隨着全球經濟開始復甦，憑中國單一的力量將不足以支撐華為。<br />\n<br />\nsource : ONcc"},{"pid":"a38d4187b04f01ebd724153ccec3ff1d7850427b","tid":2131902,"uid":25468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:40:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/30/2FnGui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F30%2F2FnGui.png&h=c345716d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/07/30/uTkdPe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F07%2F30%2FuTkdPe.png&h=a96c53cf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0d0e1f2d8317071107ac81b3cdd63e75ff6319c","tid":2131902,"uid":47259,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:42:10.000Z","msg":"出貨當賣咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 壓響D retailers倉底變蟹貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw其實唔出貨支共係咪都要磅水養住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a712b5ed9fbd62ba551366a7b